Enum Solution.Strategy

    Enclosing class:
    Solution

    public static enum Solution.Strategy
extends java.lang.Enum<Solution.Strategy>
    Different strategies available for reactive selection sequence.

    ORDERED Iterates on the elements of the solution and tries to use reactives in order of appearance. Each execution will give the same result.
    RANDOM The iteration is randomized and each execution is different (indeterminism).
